games.summary: CHARLOTTE, N.C. -- — Stephen Curry scored 26 points in his annual homecoming game in Charlotte, and the Golden State Warriors defeated the Hornets 132-125 on Wednesday in front of 19,685, the largest crowd ever at the Spectrum Center.

Jalen Johnson scored 34 points and the Atlanta Hawks overcame Anthony Edwards ' 30 points for Minnesota to beat the Timberwolves 126-102 on Wednesday and end a seven-game losing streak. The Hawks were bolstered by the return of Kristaps Porzingis , who scored 16 points in 17 minutes off the bench after missing 10 games with an illness.

Paolo Banchero had 29 points and 10 rebounds and hit the go-ahead basket with 7.5 seconds remaining as the Orlando Magic rallied from a 10-point, third-quarter deficit and beat Indiana 112-110 on Wednesday, sending the Pacers to their 10th consecutive loss. Pascal Siakam led the Pacers with 26 points.
blurbs: 📋 Johnny Furphy (IND) made just his 3rd start this season. 0 pts, 2 reb.

games.summary: Donovan Mitchell scored 34 points, Darius Garland added 19 and the Cleveland Cavaliers pulled away in the fourth quarter to defeat the Phoenix Suns 129-113 on Wednesday to snap their four-game winning streak. Evan Mobley (16 points, 10 rebounds) and Jarrett Allen (16 points, 11 rebounds) both had double-doubles.
blurbs: ⬆️ Craig Porter Jr. (CLE) played 29 min (season avg: 16). 2 pts, 9 reb, 2 ast.

games.summary: Isaac Okoro scored a season-high 24 points, Tre Jones added 20 points and 12 assists and the depleted Chicago Bulls topped the New Orleans Pelicans 134-118 on Wednesday night. Zion Williamson led New Orleans with 31 points and Jordan Poole added 26 off the bench in the team's fifth straight loss.
blurbs: 🆕 Jalen Smith (CHI) made his first start of the season. 26 min, 14 pts.
⬆️ Isaac Okoro (CHI) played 36 min (season avg: 24). 24 pts, 5 reb, 2 ast.

games.summary: Julian Champagnie had a career-high 36 points and set a franchise record with 11 3-pointers and the San Antonio Spurs survived an injury scare to Victor Wembanyama , rallying to beat the New York Knicks 134-132 on Wednesday night in a rematch of the NBA Cup final.
blurbs: 📋 Mohamed Diawara (NY) made just his 4th start this season. 6 pts, 1 reb.

games.summary: Peyton Watson scored 24 points, Jamal Murray had 21 and the Denver Nuggets won their first game without injured center Nikola Jokic , beating the Toronto Raptors 106-103 on Wednesday night. Immanuel Quickley scored 22 points and Scottie Barnes had 20 points, 14 rebounds and 10 assists for his eighth career triple-double and second in three games.
blurbs: ⬆️ Spencer Jones (DEN) played 38 min (season avg: 21). 6 pts, 7 reb, 2 ast.
🆕 Jonas Valanciunas (DEN) made his first start of the season. 23 min, 17 pts.
📋 Jalen Pickett (DEN) made just his 2nd start this season. 10 pts, 1 reb.

games.summary: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander scored 30 points in three quarters and the Oklahoma City Thunder rolled past the Portland Trail Blazers 124-95 on Wednesday night for their third straight win. He scored at least 20 points for the 105th consecutive game.
blurbs: ⬆️ Caleb Love (POR) played 30 min (season avg: 19). 10 pts, 5 reb, 4 ast.
